author: olegk
msg: PR #33468 (httpclient doesn't read and parse response from certain types of proxy servers when POST method is used)
HttpClient no longer flushes the request line and request headers prior to writing the request body if the 'expect: continue' handshake is not used.
Contributed by Peter Tolmachov <peter.tolmachov at agfa.com>
Reviewed by Oleg Kalnichevski, Michael Becke
